metadata.description: Weber Inc., an outdoor cooking company, manufactures and distributes outdoor cooking products, accessories, consumables, and services in North America, Europe, Australia, and internationally. Its products include charcoal and gas grills, smokers, pellet and electric grills, and Weber Connect Smart Grilling Hub; and accessories, consumables, and services. The company sells its products through omni-channel network comprising wholesale, direct-to-consumer, and e-commerce channels. Weber Inc. was founded in 1952 and is headquartered in Palatine, Illinois.
